		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Short answer: one step in one cycle.
<br />Long answer: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdevwiki.ath.cx/index.php/NES_PPU#Sprite_evaluation">http://nesdevwiki.ath.cx/index.php/NES_ ... evaluation</a><!-- m -->

		

